01:02:31,796 --> 01:02:35,096
不可知の底で一人
Alone at the bottom of the unknown

1328
01:02:35,096 --> 01:02:37,846
扉と鍵を探す
Searching for the door and key

1329
01:02:38,346 --> 01:02:40,896
お伽噺はほら
Fairy tales are, look...

1330
01:02:41,396 --> 01:02:43,996
泡のように全部消えて
Disappearing like bubbles

1331
01:02:44,246 --> 01:02:46,996
葛藤 残像だけ
Only conflict and afterimages

1332
01:02:48,396 --> 01:02:50,096
次のページへ
To the next page

1333
01:02:51,696 --> 01:02:55,796
伸びてく枝葉が別れて
The extending branches and leaves separate

1334
01:02:56,696 --> 01:03:00,096
それぞれの道を行く
Going their separate ways

1335
01:03:01,896 --> 01:03:05,796
寂しい思い出だけが
Only lonely memories

1336
01:03:06,696 --> 01:03:09,596
強く根を張ってる
Are rooting deeply

1337
01:03:14,396 --> 01:03:16,896
まだ貫いて失って
Still piercing through and losing

1338
01:03:16,896 --> 01:03:19,096
それでも挫けない
But still not discouraged

1339
01:03:19,096 --> 01:03:22,096
心は何処に 器は何処に
Where is the heart? Where is the vessel?

1340
01:03:24,496 --> 01:03:27,296
ただ残されて抜け落ちて
Just left behind and falling out

1341
01:03:27,296 --> 01:03:29,296
それでも伝えたいよ
But I still want to convey it

1342
01:03:29,296 --> 01:03:32,296
魂の日々は 魂の意志は
The days of the soul, the will of the soul

1343
01:03:32,496 --> 01:03:35,896
ずっと... Woah woah...
Forever... Woah woah...

1344
01:04:06,496 --> 01:04:09,096
魂の色は何色ですか
What color is the soul?

1345
01:04:11,196 --> 01:04:14,096
何色ですか...
What color is it...

1346
01:04:16,296 --> 01:04:19,096
赤い色ですか
Is it red?

1347
01:04:21,096 --> 01:04:24,096
青い色ですか
Is it blue?

1348
01:04:26,196 --> 01:04:29,096
魂の色は...
The color of the soul is...

1349
01:04:36,246 --> 01:04:40,496
透明な過去に 不透明な明日に
In the transparent past, in the opaque tomorrow

1350
01:04:41,196 --> 01:04:44,346
生きるあなたは何色ですか
What color are you, who lives?

1351
01:04:47,546 --> 01:04:50,246
また躓いて転がって
Stumbling and rolling again

1352
01:04:50,246 --> 01:04:52,296
それでも砕けない
But still unbreakable

1353
01:04:52,296 --> 01:04:56,596
魂の色は何色ですか
What color is the soul?

1354
01:04:57,996 --> 01:04:59,996
ただ傷ついて強がって...
Just getting hurt and acting tough...

1355
01:05:00,744 --> 01:05:01,904
見つけたよ
I found it.

1356
01:05:02,204 --> 01:05:04,104
魂の形
The shape of the soul.

1357
01:05:04,354 --> 01:05:06,754
確かめてるよ
I'm confirming it.

1358
01:05:07,004 --> 01:05:08,304
ずっと...
Always...

1359
01:05:08,304 --> 01:05:12,104
ウォー...
Woah...

1360
01:05:16,604 --> 01:05:17,904
ずっと...
Always...

1361
